reviewText: It's an awesome product. Like with the first disc collector's set, I was a little disappointed with the language (I was expecting a japanese track) but that's all the problems I had. Love the series!

I just got the 1st and 2nd collector's set, today. They are awesome. Moomin is a great cartoon to watch with your kids.

I know British dubbed 52 episodes out of 78 episodes. So, there are still 28 more episodes to go. I really want to see them all.
this show reminds me of some of the cartoons made in the 80's. Pure, innocent yet intresting and Fun stories that all people can injoy. You fall in love with each character.
